    <string name="disclaimer_titulo">Legal Notice and Terms of Use.</string>
    <string name="disclaimer_texto">This application has been developed for educational and informational purposes, aimed at an adult audience and is intended as a guiding tool for calculating Body Mass Index (BMI) in both adults and minors under 20 years of age.\n\nMEDICAL AND PROFESSIONAL USE\n• Does not replace the opinion of a healthcare professional.\n• Calculated values and interpretations provided are guiding and should not be considered medical diagnoses.\n• In case of health concerns, always consult with a doctor or pediatrician.\n\nABOUT 5 TO 19 YEARS OF AGE\n• BMI in minors under 20 years of age is not interpreted the same as in adults.\n• BMI calculation in minors under 20 years of age is based on WHO references.\n• This application is not designed to evaluate the development of children under 5 years of age.\n\nPRIVACY AND SECURITY\n• This application does not collect or transmit personal data to external servers.\n• All information is stored locally on the device, without encryption.\n\nUSER RESPONSIBILITY\n• The user is solely responsible for the use of this application.\n• Using this application implies acceptance of these terms.</string>
